Hyde Park Prime Steakhouse is an award-winning, prime steakhouse specializing in aged USDA prime steaks. Located in the heart of Birmingham, Detroits most popular pedestrian-friendly suburb for dining and shopping, the restaurant offers a chef-inspired menu featuring variations of its legendary aged prime steaks, daily chefs fresh fish features and great seafood. Walking distance to the Palladium, Birmingham 8 Theater. Award-winning menus, the extensive wine list and impeccable service are why Hyde Park Prime Steakhouse is metro Detroits top-rated fine dining restaurant for intimate dinners, special occasions, business meetings, corporate events and small receptions.

The most recent visit, it took over an hour for two of our appetizers, 30 mins for bread, and it wasn't clear if we were being charged for "Water." Not sure who our waiter was, I don't remember if he even left a name, but he never asked how was the food, dining experience or anything. When we left he said Thanks and kept walking....very poor service. I would think there's a standard being in Birmingham, but I'm not from here so I don't know. Being a native Chicagoan, service is at the top of my list, so I guess I'll give them a pass this time. Great food though.

                                                                          Privacy Preference Center

                                                                          When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer. For additional information, please visit our Cookies Policy and our Privacy Policy.

                                                                          Always Active

                                                                          These cookies are necessary for our site to function and cannot be switched off. They are usually set in response to your actions, like setting your privacy preferences, creating an account, or logging in. You can set your browser to block these cookies, but some parts of the site will then not work.

                                                                          Performance Cookies

                                                                          These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.

                                                                          Functional Cookies

                                                                          These cookies enable our site to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or third-party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.

                                                                          Targeting Cookies

                                                                          These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
